HEADWORD: Arid
<hw>Ar"id</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>aridus</ets>,
fr. <ets>arere</ets> to be dry: cf. F. <ets>aride</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Exhausted of moisture; parched with heat; dry; barren.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧An <xex>arid</xex> waste.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Thomson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

